[SN]TITLE[SN]
Is this the world's coldest golf course?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Golfers in Russia don't let the freezing weather stop them enjoying their sport - they play on a massive frozen lake!

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
14 March 2017 Last updated at 17:37 GMT
Fifty people turned up to take part in the 'ice golf' tournament which happens every year on the frozen Lake Baikal.
The rules are just the same as normal golf, except that the balls are red to show up against the snow.
